1) An api kind of design is created where an api for playing battleship game is provided thru two interfaces namely 
   IPlayGameApi.java and IConverterApi.java
   
   Variety of clients can be created which can access these apis to develop the game. For example, This code created a command line 
   client using these apis.
   
2) State along with factory design pattern is used to implement each moves of a Ship

